# 🏦 Business Requirements.                              

## 📌 Business Scenario Summary                                                                                         

Unity Bank Uganda *(Fictional)* has experienced increasing operational workloads across its retail banking operations.

Senior management requires a centralized dashboard to monitor case volumes, analyst productivity, branch performance, SLA compliance, and operational efficiency.

This dashboard is designed to support data-driven operational decision-making.

---

## ❓ Business Questions

### Executive View

- How many cases did we receive?
- How many have been completed?
- How many are still open?
- Are we meeting our SLA?
- Which branches are performing well?
- Which branches need attention?

### Analyst Performance

- Which analyst closes the most cases?
- Which analyst has the longest turnaround time?
- Who has the biggest backlog?

### Operations

- Which products generate the most requests?
- Which case types take the longest?
- Which regions have the highest workload?
- Are escalations increasing?          

###  Customer

- Which customer segment raises the most requests?
- Which requests are highest risk?





          
